title: Handshake Light Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Two hands meeting in the middle, signifying agreement, greeting, or a deal being made between people with light to medium skin tones.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the handshake: light skin tone, medium skin tone emoji showcases a firm and welcoming connection with its dynamic 3D rendering. The interlocking hands, depicted with Apple's characteristic realistic lighting and soft rounded edges, convey trust, agreement, and partnership. This emoji's clean lines and smooth gradients make it a universally understood symbol of collaboration and good faith.
